<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4401761>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 3. Habitus (A–E), male genitalia (F–I), and attached labels (G, H) of Pterostichus marginatus marginatus (A–C, F, G, J, K) and P. m. subrugosus (D, E, H, I). A, dorsal view of syntype male; B, dorsal view of syntype female; C, dorsal view of male from Porechje envir., Sakhalin; D, dorsal view of male from Kumono-daira; E, dorsal view of female from Kumono-daira; F, H, right lateral view of everted endophallus; G, I, left lateral view of everted endophallus; J, label attached to syntype male; K, labels attached to syntype female. dl, dorsal lob; gp, gonopore; ll, left lateral lobe; lv-1, basal sub-lobe of left ventral lobe; lv-2, apical sub-lobe of left ventral lobe; rv-1, basal sub-lobe of right ventral lobe; rv-2, apical sub-lobe of right ventral lobe." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4401761/files/figure.png" .

